Zandile Msutwana (a mụrụ na 6 Julaị 1979 na King William's Town) bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri na South Africa nke a maara nke ọma maka ọrụ ya dịka Akua Yenana n'afọ 2007- 2010 SABC 1 drama series Society
E debara aha ya na UCT ebe o nwetara diplọma ndị na-eme ihe nkiri na Speech and Drama
Msutwana malitere ọrụ ime ihe nkiri ya mgbe ọ nọ na mahadum, ebe ọ pụtara na mmepụta dịka; King Lear, The Suit, Brink, Trojan Women.
Ọrụ ime ihe nkiri ya malitere n'afọ 2007 ebe ọ gosipụtara ọrụ dị mkpa na usoro ihe nkiri SABC 1 Society
Ọ rụrụ ọrụ dịka Akua Yenana, onye na-ere ahịa na mgbe ahụ nwanyị ntụrụndụ ruo mgbe ọ hapụrụ n'afọ 2010.
N'afọ 2009, ọ rụrụ ọrụ dịka nwanyị a na-alụ ọhụrụ, Ayanda, na ihe nkiri White Wedding ya na Kenneth Nkosi, nwoke na-alụ nwanyị ọhụrụ, na Rapulana Seiphemo, nwoke kachasị mma.
N'afọ 2013, ọ rụrụ ọrụ dị mkpa na Zabalaza nke Mzansi Magic ruo mgbe ọ hapụrụ n'afọ 2015 nke gosipụtara Baby Cele.

N'afọ 2016, na usoro ihe nkiri nke Mzansi Magic bụ Isikizi; ọ pụtara dịka Nomazwe, nne na-amụ nwa eze nke Sangoma (onye na-agwọ ọrịa ọdịnala) kwupụtara dịka nwa ọhụrụ a bụrụ ọnụ nke ga-etolite igbu nna ya ma lụọ nne ya.
Ọ rụrụ ọrụ nke adaeze Nomakhwezi na Igazi's Season 1, Shona na Connie Ferguson mmepụta, n'akụkụ Vatiswa Ndara, Jet Novuka na Nomhle Nkonyeni nwụrụ anwụ.
Ọ na-arụ ọrụ dị mkpa nke Vuyiswa Jola na The Queen, ya na Shona Ferguson na Connie Ferguson.
Ihe nkiri telivishọn ndị ọzọ ya gụnyere Home Affairs, Mtunzini.com, Isidingo, Rhythm City na Soul City
na ihe nkiri ndị ọzọ ya na-agụnye The Algiers Murders na A Small Town Called Descent
A họpụtara ya na SAFTA Golden Horn: Best Supporting Actress award n'afọ 2010 maka ọrụ ya na ihe nkiri White Wedding nke 2009.
